story.text: Going to watch Wonder Woman tonight in 3D. Wooooo. Should be fun. Wish I had my contacts. Oh wait, I do. Because I am always prepared ;).

Rough chat with Leigh last night. I tried to explain that I cannot force myself to enjoy time with people who do not support my drive in life - what more can I say. She misses the old me. I like the new me, and wish she would adapt, if she truly loves me.
Kamila gets me. It is nice. Comfortable. I hope that I do not disappoint her.
